title: American horror story murder house - violet finds out she's dead
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: Finding out that Violet have died like 3 episodes ago was the biggest plot twist of my life
Honestly, Can you ever imagine what if after death we might be standing right next to our loving ones , hear them talking but can't talk or touch them.
The only humanly decent thing Tate did was try to get Violet to live so she wouldn't die in the house. That was actually decent.
The dog barking at the Violet (ghost) was so smart!
It’s sad to think about how Evan peters had to go to therapy because when he played Tate he was so messed up from it
description: American horror story murder house - violet finds out she's dead/ Tate shows violet her corpse
